item.title: CVE-2022-43393|2024-08-03T13:32:57.958Z -- zyxel -- gs1920-24v2%20firmware
item.description: An improper check for unusual or exceptional conditions in the HTTP request processing function of Zyxel GS1920-24v2 firmware prior to V4.70(ABMH.8)C0, which could allow an unauthenticated attacker to corrupt the contents of the memory and result in a denial-of-service (DoS) condition on a vulnerable device.
